    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the development and management of methods and systems to prevent, prepare for, deal with, and recover from disasters. Typically used in the context of governmental or institutional plans and programs. For planning by individuals, families, or other small groups, prefer "emergency preparedness."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
